snippet.title: Secret Santa - Doki Doki Blue Skies Teaser #8 (Yuri's Route)
snippet.description:
Merry Christmas from Blue Skies!

The girls all spend Christmas at the MC's house and exchange Secret Santa gifts. 

This is a part of Yuri's route. Each route has Christmas play out a little differently, so be sure to check them all out with the full release!

Join the Discord. Chat with the devs and keep updated with mod updates! 

https://discordapp.com/invite/yUgz578

Twitter: twitter.com/blueskiesmod

Website: COMING SOON!
